<L>__{interior art's donut hole}
<A>__{a few people linger over coffee. the waitress serving them is monica (the same but younger woman from lovin' oven). in a corner, michael fitzsimmons, in a red leather jacket, sits alone, reading. he looks up to check on his motorcycle parked outside. he's splendid in his isolation. peggy enters, taking a seat at the counter, startled to see monica, who doesn't know her.}
<C>__{monica}
<D>__{what would you like?}
