<D>__{maybe you're confusing his life with his work.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{a writer's life is his work. jack kerouac doesn't have to kill a bull to have something to write about. he's out there feeling, burning... grooving on life!}
<A>__{michael leans back in his chair. he's said his piece. peggy studies him for a beat.}
